description:
September 9, 2019 / A Ukrainian nuclear scientist and his wife are murdered in cold blood on a hot August night in 1998 in rural Tennessee. Investigators have little evidence to go on, yet manage to identify a prime suspect on the very day of the murders
 
Episode scoring music by Blue Dot Sessions and Spencer Burdette.
